snippet.title: Should Amber Heard be REMOVED from Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
155,000+ people already made the move to sign a petition calling for Amber Heard to be removed from Aquaman 2 after leaked audiotapes surfaced exposing her as the one who had hit her ex-husband Johnny Depp. 

The person who created the petition did so to call people to action to take a stand against domestic violence.
The creator named Jeanne Larson, said, 
"As Amber Heard is a known and proven domestic abuser, Warner Brothers and DC Entertainment should and must remove Heard from their Aquaman 2 film project.”

Should Amber be punished like this?
